title: Associate Dean David Van Slyke to Chair Search for Next Maxwell School Dean (Syracuse University) ...
text: ( Source : Syracuse University ) Interim Vice Chancellor and Provost Liz Liddy has selected Associate Dean David Van Slyke to chair the search committee for the next dean of the Maxwell School of Citizenship and Public Affairs . David Van Slyke
